#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "dn3:1.28.13"
msgid "4. Vijjācaraṇakathā"
msgstr ""

# Acc. to comm, Ambattha assumed this was referring to his own vedic lore. Hence, in the next line, I take the āya ending as locative, in agreement with yattha below.
#. </h2><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs2.1"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.100"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc38"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.1.1"
msgid "“Katamaṃ pana taṃ, bho gotama, caraṇaṃ, katamā ca pana sā vijjā”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.1.2"
msgid ""
"“Na kho, ambaṭṭha, anuttarāya vijjācaraṇasampadāya jātivādo vā vuccati, "
"gottavādo vā vuccati, mānavādo vā vuccati:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.1.3"
msgid "‘arahasi vā maṃ tvaṃ, na vā maṃ tvaṃ arahasī’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.1.4"
msgid ""
"Yattha kho, ambaṭṭha, āvāho vā hoti, vivāho vā hoti, āvāhavivāho vā hoti, "
"etthetaṃ vuccati jātivādo vā itipi gottavādo vā itipi mānavādo vā itipi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.1.5"
msgid "‘arahasi vā maṃ tvaṃ, na vā maṃ tvaṃ arahasī’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.1.6"
msgid ""
"Ye hi keci, ambaṭṭha, jātivādavinibaddhā vā gottavādavinibaddhā vā "
"mānavādavinibaddhā vā āvāhavivāhavinibaddhā vā, ārakā te anuttarāya "
"vijjācaraṇasampadāya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.1.7"
msgid ""
"Pahāya kho, ambaṭṭha, jātivādavinibaddhañca gottavādavinibaddhañca "
"mānavādavinibaddhañca āvāhavivāhavinibaddhañca anuttarāya "
"vijjācaraṇasampadāya sacchikiriyā hotī”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs2.2"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc39"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.2.1"
msgid "“Katamaṃ pana taṃ, bho gotama, caraṇaṃ, katamā ca sā vijjā”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.2.2"
msgid ""
"“Idha, ambaṭṭha, tathāgato loke uppajjati arahaṃ sammāsambuddho "
"vijjācaraṇasampanno sugato lokavidū anuttaro purisadammasārathi satthā "
"devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.2.3"
msgid ""
"So imaṃ lokaṃ sadevakaṃ samārakaṃ sabrahmakaṃ sassamaṇabrāhmaṇiṃ pajaṃ "
"sadevamanussaṃ sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā pavedeti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.2.4"
msgid ""
"So dhammaṃ deseti ādikalyāṇaṃ majjhekalyāṇaṃ pariyosānakalyāṇaṃ sātthaṃ "
"sabyañjanaṃ kevalaparipuṇṇaṃ parisuddhaṃ brahmacariyaṃ pakāseti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.2.5"
msgid ""
"Taṃ dhammaṃ suṇāti gahapati vā gahapatiputto vā aññatarasmiṃ vā kule "
"paccājāto."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.2.6"
msgid "So taṃ dhammaṃ sutvā tathāgate saddhaṃ paṭilabhati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.2.7"
msgid "So tena saddhāpaṭilābhena samannāgato iti paṭisañcikkhati … pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc40"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.2.8"
msgid ""
"So vivicceva kāmehi, vivicca akusalehi dhammehi, savitakkaṃ savicāraṃ "
"vivekajaṃ pītisukhaṃ paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.2.9"
msgid "idampissa hoti caraṇasmiṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc41"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.2.10"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, ambaṭṭha, bhikkhu vitakkavicārānaṃ vūpasamā ajjhattaṃ "
"sampasādanaṃ cetaso ekodibhāvaṃ avitakkaṃ avicāraṃ samādhijaṃ pītisukhaṃ "
"dutiyaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.2.11"
msgid "idampissa hoti caraṇasmiṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc42"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.2.12"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, ambaṭṭha, bhikkhu pītiyā ca virāgā upekkhako ca viharati sato "
"ca sampajāno, sukhañca kāyena paṭisaṃvedeti, yaṃ taṃ ariyā ācikkhanti: ‘"
"upekkhako satimā sukhavihārī’ti, tatiyaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.2.13"
msgid "idampissa hoti caraṇasmiṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc43"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.2.14"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, ambaṭṭha, bhikkhu sukhassa ca pahānā dukkhassa ca pahānā, "
"pubbeva somanassadomanassānaṃ atthaṅgamā adukkhamasukhaṃ "
"upekkhāsatipārisuddhiṃ catutthaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.2.15"
msgid "idampissa hoti caraṇasmiṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.2.16"
msgid "Idaṃ kho taṃ, ambaṭṭha, caraṇaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc44"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.2.17"
msgid ""
"So evaṃ samāhite citte parisuddhe pariyodāte anaṅgaṇe vigatūpakkilese "
"mudubhūte kammaniye ṭhite āneñjappatte ñāṇadassanāya cittaṃ abhinīharati "
"abhininnāmeti … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.2.18"
msgid "idampissa hoti vijjāya … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.2.19"
msgid "nāparaṃ itthattāyāti pajānāti, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.2.20"
msgid "idampissa hoti vijjāya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.2.21"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho sā, ambaṭṭha, vijjā."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc45"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.2.22"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ vuccati, ambaṭṭha, bhikkhu ‘vijjāsampanno’ itipi, ‘caraṇasampanno’ "
"itipi, ‘vijjācaraṇasampanno’ itipi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.2.23"
msgid ""
"Imāya ca, ambaṭṭha, vijjāsampadāya caraṇasampadāya ca aññā vijjāsampadā ca "
"caraṇasampadā ca uttaritarā vā paṇītatarā vā natthi."
msgstr ""

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "dn3:2.2.24"
msgid "5. Catuapāyamukha"
msgstr ""

# https://discourse.suttacentral.net/t/apayamukha-in-the-ebts-doesn-t-mean-path-to-a-lower-realm/5577
#. </h2><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs2.3"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.101"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc46"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.3.1"
msgid ""
"Imāya kho, ambaṭṭha, anuttarāya vijjācaraṇasampadāya cattāri apāyamukhāni "
"bhavanti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.3.2"
msgid "Katamāni cattāri?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.3.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, ambaṭṭha, ekacco samaṇo vā brāhmaṇo vā imaññeva anuttaraṃ "
"vijjācaraṇasampadaṃ anabhisambhuṇamāno khārividhamādāya araññāyatanaṃ "
"ajjhogāhati:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.3.4"
msgid "‘pavattaphalabhojano bhavissāmī’ti."
msgstr ""

# This phrase echoes the earlier aññadatthu brāhmaṇasseva paricārakā sampajjanti
msgctxt "dn3:2.3.5"
msgid "So aññadatthu vijjācaraṇasampannasseva paricārako sampajjati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.3.6"
msgid ""
"Imāya kho, ambaṭṭha, anuttarāya vijjācaraṇasampadāya idaṃ paṭhamaṃ "
"apāyamukhaṃ bhavati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc47"></a>
#. VAR: kudālapiṭakaṃ → kuddālapiṭakaṃ (bj, s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "dn3:2.3.7"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, ambaṭṭha, idhekacco samaṇo vā brāhmaṇo vā imañceva anuttaraṃ "
"vijjācaraṇasampadaṃ anabhisambhuṇamāno pavattaphalabhojanatañca "
"anabhisambhuṇamāno kudālapiṭakaṃ ādāya araññavanaṃ ajjhogāhati:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.3.8"
msgid "‘kandamūlaphalabhojano bhavissāmī’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.3.9"
msgid "So aññadatthu vijjācaraṇasampannasseva paricārako sampajjati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.3.10"
msgid ""
"Imāya kho, ambaṭṭha, anuttarāya vijjācaraṇasampadāya idaṃ dutiyaṃ "
"apāyamukhaṃ bhavati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc48"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.3.11"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, ambaṭṭha, idhekacco samaṇo vā brāhmaṇo vā imañceva anuttaraṃ "
"vijjācaraṇasampadaṃ anabhisambhuṇamāno pavattaphalabhojanatañca "
"anabhisambhuṇamāno kandamūlaphalabhojanatañca anabhisambhuṇamāno "
"gāmasāmantaṃ vā nigamasāmantaṃ vā agyāgāraṃ karitvā aggiṃ paricaranto "
"acchati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.3.12"
msgid "So aññadatthu vijjācaraṇasampannasseva paricārako sampajjati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.3.13"
msgid ""
"Imāya kho, ambaṭṭha, anuttarāya vijjācaraṇasampadāya idaṃ tatiyaṃ "
"apāyamukhaṃ bhavati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.102"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc49"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.3.14"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, ambaṭṭha, idhekacco samaṇo vā brāhmaṇo vā imaṃ ceva anuttaraṃ "
"vijjācaraṇasampadaṃ anabhisambhuṇamāno pavattaphalabhojanatañca "
"anabhisambhuṇamāno kandamūlaphalabhojanatañca anabhisambhuṇamāno "
"aggipāricariyañca anabhisambhuṇamāno cātumahāpathe catudvāraṃ agāraṃ karitvā "
"acchati:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.3.15"
msgid ""
"‘yo imāhi catūhi disāhi āgamissati samaṇo vā brāhmaṇo vā, tamahaṃ yathāsatti "
"yathābalaṃ paṭipūjessāmī’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.3.16"
msgid "So aññadatthu vijjācaraṇasampannasseva paricārako sampajjati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.3.17"
msgid ""
"Imāya kho, ambaṭṭha, anuttarāya vijjācaraṇasampadāya idaṃ catutthaṃ "
"apāyamukhaṃ bhavati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.3.18"
msgid ""
"Imāya kho, ambaṭṭha, anuttarāya vijjācaraṇasampadāya imāni cattāri "
"apāyamukhāni bhavanti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs2.4"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc50"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.4.1"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, ambaṭṭha, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.4.2"
msgid ""
"api nu tvaṃ imāya anuttarāya vijjācaraṇasampadāya sandissasi sācariyako”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.4.3"
msgid "“No hidaṃ, bho gotama."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.4.4"
msgid "Kocāhaṃ, bho gotama, sācariyako, kā ca anuttarā vijjācaraṇasampadā?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.4.5"
msgid "Ārakāhaṃ, bho gotama, anuttarāya vijjācaraṇasampadāya sācariyako”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc51"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.4.6"
msgid "“Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, ambaṭṭha, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.4.7"
msgid ""
"api nu tvaṃ imañceva anuttaraṃ vijjācaraṇasampadaṃ anabhisambhuṇamāno "
"khārividhamādāya araññavanamajjhogāhasi sācariyako:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.4.8"
msgid "‘pavattaphalabhojano bhavissāmī’”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.4.9"
msgid "“No hidaṃ, bho gotama”."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc52"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.4.10"
msgid "“Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, ambaṭṭha, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.4.11"
msgid ""
"api nu tvaṃ imañceva anuttaraṃ vijjācaraṇasampadaṃ anabhisambhuṇamāno "
"pavattaphalabhojanatañca anabhisambhuṇamāno kudālapiṭakaṃ ādāya "
"araññavanamajjhogāhasi sācariyako:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.4.12"
msgid "‘kandamūlaphalabhojano bhavissāmī’”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.4.13"
msgid "“No hidaṃ, bho gotama”."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.103"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc53"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.4.14"
msgid "“Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, ambaṭṭha, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.4.15"
msgid ""
"api nu tvaṃ imañceva anuttaraṃ vijjācaraṇasampadaṃ anabhisambhuṇamāno "
"pavattaphalabhojanatañca anabhisambhuṇamāno kandamūlaphalabhojanatañca "
"anabhisambhuṇamāno gāmasāmantaṃ vā nigamasāmantaṃ vā agyāgāraṃ karitvā aggiṃ "
"paricaranto acchasi sācariyako”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.4.16"
msgid "“No hidaṃ, bho gotama”."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc54"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.4.17"
msgid "“Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, ambaṭṭha, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.4.18"
msgid ""
"api nu tvaṃ imañceva anuttaraṃ vijjācaraṇasampadaṃ anabhisambhuṇamāno "
"pavattaphalabhojanatañca anabhisambhuṇamāno kandamūlaphalabhojanatañca "
"anabhisambhuṇamāno aggipāricariyañca anabhisambhuṇamāno cātumahāpathe "
"catudvāraṃ agāraṃ karitvā acchasi sācariyako:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.4.19"
msgid ""
"‘yo imāhi catūhi disāhi āgamissati samaṇo vā brāhmaṇo vā, taṃ mayaṃ "
"yathāsatti yathābalaṃ paṭipūjessāmā’”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.4.20"
msgid "“No hidaṃ, bho gotama”."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs2.5"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc55"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.5.1"
msgid ""
"“Iti kho, ambaṭṭha, imāya ceva tvaṃ anuttarāya vijjācaraṇasampadāya parihīno "
"sācariyako."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.5.2"
msgid ""
"Ye cime anuttarāya vijjācaraṇasampadāya cattāri apāyamukhāni bhavanti, tato "
"ca tvaṃ parihīno sācariyako."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.5.3"
msgid ""
"Bhāsitā kho pana te esā, ambaṭṭha, ācariyena brāhmaṇena pokkharasātinā vācā:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.5.4"
msgid ""
"‘ke ca muṇḍakā samaṇakā ibbhā kaṇhā bandhupādāpaccā, kā ca tevijjānaṃ "
"brāhmaṇānaṃ sākacchā’ti attanā āpāyikopi aparipūramāno."
msgstr ""

# This harks back to Kiṃ pana te, ambaṭṭha, sakyā aparaddhum. BTW, this is a savage takedown.
msgctxt "dn3:2.5.5"
msgid ""
"Passa, ambaṭṭha, yāva aparaddhañca te idaṃ ācariyassa brāhmaṇassa "
"pokkharasātissa."
msgstr ""

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "dn3:2.5.6"
msgid "6. Pubbakaisibhāvānuyoga"
msgstr ""

#. </h2><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs2.6"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc56"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.6.1"
msgid ""
"Brāhmaṇo kho pana, ambaṭṭha, pokkharasāti rañño pasenadissa kosalassa "
"dattikaṃ bhuñjati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.6.2"
msgid "Tassa rājā pasenadi kosalo sammukhībhāvampi na dadāti."
msgstr ""

# Is this practice attested to elsewhere?
msgctxt "dn3:2.6.3"
msgid "Yadāpi tena manteti, tirodussantena manteti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.6.4"
msgid ""
"Yassa kho pana, ambaṭṭha, dhammikaṃ payātaṃ bhikkhaṃ paṭiggaṇheyya, kathaṃ "
"tassa rājā pasenadi kosalo sammukhībhāvampi na dadeyya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.6.5"
msgid ""
"Passa, ambaṭṭha, yāva aparaddhañca te idaṃ ācariyassa brāhmaṇassa "
"pokkharasātissa."
msgstr ""

# Here ugga must be a noun. See my note on AN 7.67. Rajanna is used fairly rarely in the suttas. According to the Sanskrit dicts, it is the old form of khattiya. But in the Pali it is an alternative for Khattiya. Given it’s age and association with arriors, chieftan seems apt.
#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs2.7"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.104"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc57"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.7.1"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, ambaṭṭha, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.7.2"
msgid ""
"idha rājā pasenadi kosalo hatthigīvāya vā nisinno assapiṭṭhe vā nisinno "
"rathūpatthare vā ṭhito uggehi vā rājaññehi vā kiñcideva mantanaṃ manteyya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.7.3"
msgid "So tamhā padesā apakkamma ekamantaṃ tiṭṭheyya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.7.4"
msgid ""
"Atha āgaccheyya suddo vā suddadāso vā, tasmiṃ padese ṭhito tadeva mantanaṃ "
"manteyya:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.7.5"
msgid "‘evampi rājā pasenadi kosalo āha, evampi rājā pasenadi kosalo āhā’ti."
msgstr ""

# Taking this and the next as one sentence, as per RD.
msgctxt "dn3:2.7.6"
msgid "Api nu so rājabhaṇitaṃ vā bhaṇati rājamantanaṃ vā manteti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.7.7"
msgid "Ettāvatā so assa rājā vā rājamatto vā”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.7.8"
msgid "“No hidaṃ, bho gotama”."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs2.8"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc58"></a>
#. VAR: yamataggi → yamataggī (s1-3) | yamadaggi (mr)
msgctxt "dn3:2.8.1"
msgid ""
"“Evameva kho tvaṃ, ambaṭṭha, ye te ahesuṃ brāhmaṇānaṃ pubbakā isayo mantānaṃ "
"kattāro mantānaṃ pavattāro, yesamidaṃ etarahi brāhmaṇā porāṇaṃ mantapadaṃ "
"gītaṃ pavuttaṃ samihitaṃ, tadanugāyanti tadanubhāsanti bhāsitamanubhāsanti "
"vācitamanuvācenti, seyyathidaṃ—aṭṭhako vāmako vāmadevo vessāmitto yamataggi "
"aṅgīraso bhāradvājo vāseṭṭho kassapo bhagu:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.8.2"
msgid ""
"‘tyāhaṃ mante adhiyāmi sācariyako’ti, tāvatā tvaṃ bhavissasi isi vā "
"isitthāya vā paṭipannoti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs2.9"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.105"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc59"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.9.1"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, ambaṭṭha, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.9.2"
msgid ""
"kinti te sutaṃ brāhmaṇānaṃ vuddhānaṃ mahallakānaṃ ācariyapācariyānaṃ "
"bhāsamānānaṃ—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.9.3"
msgid ""
"ye te ahesuṃ brāhmaṇānaṃ pubbakā isayo mantānaṃ kattāro mantānaṃ pavattāro, "
"yesamidaṃ etarahi brāhmaṇā porāṇaṃ mantapadaṃ gītaṃ pavuttaṃ samihitaṃ, "
"tadanugāyanti tadanubhāsanti bhāsitamanubhāsanti vācitamanuvācenti, "
"seyyathidaṃ—aṭṭhako vāmako vāmadevo vessāmitto yamataggi aṅgīraso bhāradvājo "
"vāseṭṭho kassapo bhagu,"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.9.4"
msgid ""
"evaṃ su te sunhātā suvilittā kappitakesamassū āmukkamaṇikuṇḍalābharaṇā "
"odātavatthavasanā pañcahi kāmaguṇehi samappitā samaṅgībhūtā paricārenti, "
"seyyathāpi tvaṃ etarahi sācariyako”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.9.5"
msgid "“No hidaṃ, bho gotama”."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs2.10"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc60"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.10.1"
msgid "“… pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.10.2"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ su te sālīnaṃ odanaṃ sucimaṃsūpasecanaṃ vicitakāḷakaṃ anekasūpaṃ "
"anekabyañjanaṃ paribhuñjanti, seyyathāpi tvaṃ etarahi sācariyako”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.10.3"
msgid "“No hidaṃ, bho gotama”."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc61"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.10.4"
msgid "“… pe …"
msgstr ""

# veṭhakanatapassāhi is otherwise unattested. At MN 55 veṭhaka evidently means “collar”. The Lokuttaravada Bhikshuni Vinaya has a rule about this, Pn 3: https://suttacentral.net/skt/skt-lo-bi-pn3. Thullananda gets out of the water and wraps herself only in a vethaka. Here this seems to be synonymous with paṭṭaka, i.e. a strip of cloth. It is allowable if used to tie on a basket, etc. Edgerton’s BHS dict does not notice this occurrence, but says of a ref in Mahavastu “something that wraps, covers: in a list of goldsmith’s products”, noting however a number of variants. Nata is “curve”, passa is “side, flank”. MW has “flounces and furbelows”, RD “fringes and furbelows round their loins”. These are hopelessly prissy descriptions of what sounds like the clothes of a stripper or lap-dancer.
msgctxt "dn3:2.10.5"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ su te veṭhakanatapassāhi nārīhi paricārenti, seyyathāpi tvaṃ etarahi "
"sācariyako”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.10.6"
msgid "“No hidaṃ, bho gotama”."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc62"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.10.7"
msgid "“… pe …"
msgstr ""

# This harks back to the opening of the sutta. vitudenti vitacchenti recurs at SN 19.1, of a bird being chased and pecked at by other birds. vitudenti by itself has the same meaning at Bu Pj 4. Evidently the Buddha was pretty disgusted with this maltreatment of the poor beasts.
msgctxt "dn3:2.10.8"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ su te kuttavālehi vaḷavārathehi dīghāhi patodalaṭṭhīhi vāhane vitudentā "
"vipariyāyanti, seyyathāpi tvaṃ etarahi sācariyako”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.10.9"
msgid "“No hidaṃ, bho gotama”."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc63"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.10.10"
msgid "“… pe …"
msgstr ""

#. VAR: dīghāsivudhehi → dīghāsi­bad­dhehi (bj, s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "dn3:2.10.11"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ su te ukkiṇṇaparikhāsu okkhittapalighāsu nagarūpakārikāsu "
"dīghāsivudhehi purisehi rakkhāpenti, seyyathāpi tvaṃ etarahi sācariyako”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.10.12"
msgid "“No hidaṃ, bho gotama”."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc64"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.10.13"
msgid "“Iti kho, ambaṭṭha, neva tvaṃ isi na isitthāya paṭipanno sācariyako."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.10.14"
msgid ""
"Yassa kho pana, ambaṭṭha, mayi kaṅkhā vā vimati vā so maṃ pañhena, ahaṃ "
"veyyākaraṇena sodhissāmī”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "dn3:2.10.15"
msgid "7. Dvelakkhaṇādassana"
msgstr ""

#. </h2><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs2.11"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.106"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc65"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.11.1"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā vihārā nikkhamma caṅkamaṃ abbhuṭṭhāsi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.11.2"
msgid "Ambaṭṭhopi māṇavo vihārā nikkhamma caṅkamaṃ abbhuṭṭhāsi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.11.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho ambaṭṭho māṇavo bhagavantaṃ caṅkamantaṃ anucaṅkamamāno bhagavato "
"kāye dvattiṃsamahāpurisalakkhaṇāni samannesi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.11.4"
msgid ""
"Addasā kho ambaṭṭho māṇavo bhagavato kāye dvattiṃsamahāpurisalakkhaṇāni "
"yebhuyyena ṭhapetvā dve."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.11.5"
msgid ""
"Dvīsu mahāpurisalakkhaṇesu kaṅkhati vicikicchati nādhimuccati na sampasīdati—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.11.6"
msgid "kosohite ca vatthaguyhe pahūtajivhatāya ca."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs2.12"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc66"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.12.1"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavato etadahosi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.12.2"
msgid ""
"“passati kho me ayaṃ ambaṭṭho māṇavo dvattiṃsamahāpurisalakkhaṇāni "
"yebhuyyena ṭhapetvā dve."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.12.3"
msgid ""
"Dvīsu mahāpurisalakkhaṇesu kaṅkhati vicikicchati nādhimuccati na sampasīdati—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.12.4"
msgid "kosohite ca vatthaguyhe pahūtajivhatāya cā”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.12.5"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhagavā tathārūpaṃ iddhābhisaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkhāsi. Yathā addasa "
"ambaṭṭho māṇavo bhagavato kosohitaṃ vatthaguyhaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.12.6"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhagavā jivhaṃ ninnāmetvā ubhopi kaṇṇasotāni anumasi paṭimasi, "
"ubhopi nāsikasotāni anumasi paṭimasi, kevalampi nalāṭamaṇḍalaṃ jivhāya "
"chādesi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.12.7"
msgid "Atha kho ambaṭṭhassa māṇavassa etadahosi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.12.8"
msgid ""
"“samannāgato kho samaṇo gotamo dvattiṃsamahāpurisalakkhaṇehi paripuṇṇehi, no "
"aparipuṇṇehī”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.12.9"
msgid "Bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.12.10"
msgid ""
"“handa ca dāni mayaṃ, bho gotama, gacchāma, bahukiccā mayaṃ bahukaraṇīyā”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.12.11"
msgid "“Yassadāni tvaṃ, ambaṭṭha, kālaṃ maññasī”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.12.12"
msgid "Atha kho ambaṭṭho māṇavo vaḷavārathamāruyha pakkāmi."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs2.13"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc67"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.13.1"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena brāhmaṇo pokkharasāti ukkaṭṭhāya nikkhamitvā mahatā "
"brāhmaṇagaṇena saddhiṃ sake ārāme nisinno hoti ambaṭṭhaṃyeva māṇavaṃ "
"paṭimānento."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.13.2"
msgid "Atha kho ambaṭṭho māṇavo yena sako ārāmo tena pāyāsi."
msgstr ""

#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs2.14"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.107"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc68"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.14.1"
msgid ""
"Yāvatikā yānassa bhūmi, yānena gantvā yānā paccorohitvā pattikova yena "
"brāhmaṇo pokkharasāti tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā brāhmaṇaṃ pokkharasātiṃ "
"abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho ambaṭṭhaṃ māṇavaṃ "
"brāhmaṇo pokkharasāti etadavoca:"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "dn3:2.14.2"
msgid "“kacci, tāta ambaṭṭha, addasa taṃ bhavantaṃ gotaman”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.14.3"
msgid "“Addasāma kho mayaṃ, bho, taṃ bhavantaṃ gotaman”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.14.4"
msgid ""
"“Kacci, tāta ambaṭṭha, taṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ tathā santaṃyeva saddo "
"abbhuggato no aññathā;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.14.5"
msgid "kacci pana so bhavaṃ gotamo tādiso no aññādiso”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.14.6"
msgid ""
"“Tathā santaṃyeva, bho, taṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ saddo abbhuggato no aññathā, "
"tādisova so bhavaṃ gotamo no aññādiso."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.14.7"
msgid ""
"Samannāgato ca so bhavaṃ gotamo dvattiṃsamahāpurisalakkhaṇehi paripuṇṇehi no "
"aparipuṇṇehī”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.14.8"
msgid ""
"“Ahu pana te, tāta ambaṭṭha, samaṇena gotamena saddhiṃ kocideva "
"kathāsallāpo”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.14.9"
msgid "“Ahu kho me, bho, samaṇena gotamena saddhiṃ kocideva kathāsallāpo”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.14.10"
msgid ""
"“Yathā kathaṃ pana te, tāta ambaṭṭha, ahu samaṇena gotamena saddhiṃ kocideva "
"kathāsallāpo”ti?"
msgstr ""

#. VAR: yāvatako → yāvatiko (mr)
msgctxt "dn3:2.14.11"
msgid ""
"Atha kho ambaṭṭho māṇavo yāvatako ahosi bhagavatā saddhiṃ kathāsallāpo, taṃ "
"sabbaṃ brāhmaṇassa pokkharasātissa ārocesi."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs2.15"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc69"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.15.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, brāhmaṇo pokkharasāti ambaṭṭhaṃ māṇavaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""

# The diminutive ending here is the same as the in samanaka, which Ambattha used of the Buddha. As for using bloody for re; if we don’t use curse words here, when do we get to use them!
#. VAR: tevijjaka → tevijjakā (mr)
msgctxt "dn3:2.15.2"
msgid ""
"“aho vata re amhākaṃ, paṇḍitaka, aho vata re amhākaṃ, bahussutaka, aho vata "
"re amhākaṃ, tevijjaka, evarūpena kira, bho, puriso atthacarakena kāyassa "
"bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjeyya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.15.3"
msgid ""
"Yadeva kho tvaṃ, ambaṭṭha, taṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ evaṃ āsajja āsajja avacāsi, "
"atha kho so bhavaṃ gotamo amhepi evaṃ upaneyya upaneyya avaca."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: kupito → so kupito (pts1)
msgctxt "dn3:2.15.4"
msgid ""
"Aho vata re amhākaṃ, paṇḍitaka, aho vata re amhākaṃ, bahussutaka, aho vata "
"re amhākaṃ, tevijjaka, evarūpena kira, bho, puriso atthacarakena kāyassa "
"bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjeyyā”ti, kupito "
"anattamano ambaṭṭhaṃ māṇavaṃ padasāyeva pavattesi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.15.5"
msgid "Icchati ca tāvadeva bhagavantaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamituṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "dn3:2.15.6"
msgid "8. Pokkharasātibuddhūpasaṅkamana"
msgstr ""

#. </h2><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs2.16"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.108"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc70"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.16.1"
msgid "Atha kho te brāhmaṇā brāhmaṇaṃ pokkharasātiṃ etadavocuṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.16.2"
msgid "“ativikālo kho, bho, ajja samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamituṃ."
msgstr ""

# Given his mood, this was very diplomatic of them!
#. VAR: Svedāni → dāni sve (mr)
msgctxt "dn3:2.16.3"
msgid ""
"Svedāni bhavaṃ pokkharasāti samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamissatī”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.16.4"
msgid ""
"Atha kho brāhmaṇo pokkharasāti sake nivesane paṇītaṃ khādanīyaṃ bhojanīyaṃ "
"paṭiyādāpetvā yāne āropetvā ukkāsu dhāriyamānāsu ukkaṭṭhāya niyyāsi, yena "
"icchānaṅgalavanasaṇḍo tena pāyāsi."
msgstr ""

#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs2.17"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc71"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.17.1"
msgid ""
"Yāvatikā yānassa bhūmi yānena gantvā, yānā paccorohitvā pattikova yena "
"bhagavā tenupasaṅkami. upasaṅkamitvā bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi, sammodanīyaṃ "
"kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho "
"brāhmaṇo pokkharasāti bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. VAR: te → tedha (s1-3) | te idha (pts1)
msgctxt "dn3:2.17.2"
msgid "“āgamā nu khvidha, bho gotama, amhākaṃ antevāsī ambaṭṭho māṇavo”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.17.3"
msgid "“Āgamā kho te, brāhmaṇa, antevāsī ambaṭṭho māṇavo”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.17.4"
msgid ""
"“Ahu pana te, bho gotama, ambaṭṭhena māṇavena saddhiṃ kocideva "
"kathāsallāpo”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.17.5"
msgid ""
"“Ahu kho me, brāhmaṇa, ambaṭṭhena māṇavena saddhiṃ kocideva kathāsallāpo”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.17.6"
msgid ""
"“Yathākathaṃ pana te, bho gotama, ahu ambaṭṭhena māṇavena saddhiṃ kocideva "
"kathāsallāpo”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.17.7"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhagavā yāvatako ahosi ambaṭṭhena māṇavena saddhiṃ kathāsallāpo, "
"taṃ sabbaṃ brāhmaṇassa pokkharasātissa ārocesi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.17.8"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, brāhmaṇo pokkharasāti bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.17.9"
msgid ""
"“bālo, bho gotama, ambaṭṭho māṇavo, khamatu bhavaṃ gotamo ambaṭṭhassa "
"māṇavassā”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.17.10"
msgid "“Sukhī hotu, brāhmaṇa, ambaṭṭho māṇavo”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs2.18"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.109"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc72"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.18.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho brāhmaṇo pokkharasāti bhagavato kāye dvattiṃsamahāpurisalakkhaṇāni "
"samannesi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.18.2"
msgid ""
"Addasā kho brāhmaṇo pokkharasāti bhagavato kāye "
"dvattiṃsamahāpurisalakkhaṇāni yebhuyyena ṭhapetvā dve."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.18.3"
msgid ""
"Dvīsu mahāpurisalakkhaṇesu kaṅkhati vicikicchati nādhimuccati na sampasīdati—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.18.4"
msgid "kosohite ca vatthaguyhe pahūtajivhatāya ca."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc73"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.18.5"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavato etadahosi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.18.6"
msgid ""
"“passati kho me ayaṃ brāhmaṇo pokkharasāti dvattiṃsamahāpurisalakkhaṇāni "
"yebhuyyena ṭhapetvā dve."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.18.7"
msgid ""
"Dvīsu mahāpurisalakkhaṇesu kaṅkhati vicikicchati nādhimuccati na sampasīdati—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.18.8"
msgid "kosohite ca vatthaguyhe pahūtajivhatāya cā”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.18.9"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhagavā tathārūpaṃ iddhābhisaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkhāsi yathā addasa "
"brāhmaṇo pokkharasāti bhagavato kosohitaṃ vatthaguyhaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.18.10"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhagavā jivhaṃ ninnāmetvā ubhopi kaṇṇasotāni anumasi paṭimasi, "
"ubhopi nāsikasotāni anumasi paṭimasi, kevalampi nalāṭamaṇḍalaṃ jivhāya "
"chādesi."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs2.19"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc74"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.19.1"
msgid "Atha kho brāhmaṇassa pokkharasātissa etadahosi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.19.2"
msgid ""
"“samannāgato kho samaṇo gotamo dvattiṃsamahāpurisalakkhaṇehi paripuṇṇehi no "
"aparipuṇṇehī”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.19.3"
msgid "Bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.19.4"
msgid ""
"“adhivāsetu me bhavaṃ gotamo ajjatanāya bhattaṃ saddhiṃ bhikkhusaṅghenā”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.19.5"
msgid "Adhivāsesi bhagavā tuṇhībhāvena."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs2.20"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc75"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.20.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho brāhmaṇo pokkharasāti bhagavato adhivāsanaṃ viditvā bhagavato kālaṃ "
"ārocesi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.20.2"
msgid "“kālo, bho gotama, niṭṭhitaṃ bhattan”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.20.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhagavā pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya saddhiṃ "
"bhikkhusaṅghena yena brāhmaṇassa pokkharasātissa nivesanaṃ tenupasaṅkami; "
"upasaṅkamitvā paññatte āsane nisīdi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.20.4"
msgid ""
"Atha kho brāhmaṇo pokkharasāti bhagavantaṃ paṇītena khādanīyena bhojanīyena "
"sahatthā santappesi sampavāresi, māṇavakāpi bhikkhusaṅghaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.20.5"
msgid ""
"Atha kho brāhmaṇo pokkharasāti bhagavantaṃ bhuttāviṃ onītapattapāṇiṃ "
"aññataraṃ nīcaṃ āsanaṃ gahetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs2.21"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.110"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc76"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.21.1"
msgid ""
"Ekamantaṃ nisinnassa kho brāhmaṇassa pokkharasātissa bhagavā anupubbiṃ "
"kathaṃ kathesi,"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.21.2"
msgid "seyyathidaṃ—dānakathaṃ sīlakathaṃ saggakathaṃ;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.21.3"
msgid "kāmānaṃ ādīnavaṃ okāraṃ saṅkilesaṃ, nekkhamme ānisaṃsaṃ pakāsesi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.21.4"
msgid ""
"Yadā bhagavā aññāsi brāhmaṇaṃ pokkharasātiṃ kallacittaṃ muducittaṃ "
"vinīvaraṇacittaṃ udaggacittaṃ pasannacittaṃ, atha yā buddhānaṃ sāmukkaṃsikā "
"dhammadesanā, taṃ pakāsesi—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.21.5"
msgid "dukkhaṃ samudayaṃ nirodhaṃ maggaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.21.6"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi nāma suddhaṃ vatthaṃ apagatakāḷakaṃ sammadeva rajanaṃ "
"paṭiggaṇheyya;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.21.7"
msgid ""
"evameva brāhmaṇassa pokkharasātissa tasmiññeva āsane virajaṃ vītamalaṃ "
"dhammacakkhuṃ udapādi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.21.8"
msgid "“yaṃ kiñci samudayadhammaṃ sabbaṃ taṃ nirodhadhamman”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "dn3:2.21.9"
msgid "9. Pokkharasātiupāsakattapaṭivedanā"
msgstr ""

#. </h2><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs2.22"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc77"></a>
msgctxt "dn3:2.22.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho brāhmaṇo pokkharasāti diṭṭhadhammo pattadhammo viditadhammo "
"pariyogāḷhadhammo tiṇṇavicikiccho vigatakathaṃkatho vesārajjappatto "
"aparappaccayo satthusāsane bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.22.2"
msgid "“abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama, abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.22.3"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bho gotama, nikkujjitaṃ vā ukkujjeyya, paṭicchannaṃ vā "
"vivareyya, mūḷhassa vā maggaṃ ācikkheyya, andhakāre vā telapajjotaṃ dhāreyya:"
" ‘cakkhumanto rūpāni dakkhantī’ti; evamevaṃ bhotā gotamena anekapariyāyena "
"dhammo pakāsito."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.22.4"
msgid ""
"Esāhaṃ, bho gotama, saputto sabhariyo sapariso sāmacco bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ "
"saraṇaṃ gacchāmi dhammañca bhikkhusaṃghañca."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.22.5"
msgid "Upāsakaṃ maṃ bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gataṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.22.6"
msgid ""
"Yathā ca bhavaṃ gotamo ukkaṭṭhāya aññāni upāsakakulāni upasaṅkamati, evameva "
"bhavaṃ gotamo pokkharasātikulaṃ upasaṅkamatu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.22.7"
msgid ""
"Tattha ye te māṇavakā vā māṇavikā vā bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ abhivādessanti vā "
"paccuṭṭhissanti vā āsanaṃ vā udakaṃ vā dassanti cittaṃ vā pasādessanti, "
"tesaṃ taṃ bhavissati dīgharattaṃ hitāya sukhāyā”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn3:2.22.8"
msgid "“Kalyāṇaṃ vuccati, brāhmaṇā”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "dn3:2.22.9"
msgid "Ambaṭṭhasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
